<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bill's Barber Shop - Ghostcat Challenge</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <div class="army-stripes"></div>
            <h1>🪖 Bill Dauterive's Army Surplus & Barber Shop 🪖</h1>
            <div class="army-stripes"></div>
            
            <nav style="margin-top: 20px;">
                <a href="index.jsp" style="color: #8B4513; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-weight: bold;">🏠 Home</a>
                <a href="classified.jsp" style="color: #B22222; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px; font-weight: bold;">🔒 Secret Files</a>
            </nav>
        </header>
        
        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="bill-info">
                <div class="bill-portrait">
                    <div class="bill-face">
                        <div class="glasses">👓</div>
                        <div class="mustache">👨‍🦲</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="welcome-message">
                    <h2>Welcome to Bill's Place, I tell you what!</h2>
                    <p class="bill-quote">"That's my barber shop, I don't know you!"</p>
                    <p>Serving the finest haircuts in Arlen, Texas since... well, since I got out of the Army.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="services">
                <h3>🇺🇸 Bill's Military-Grade Services 🇺🇸</h3>
                <div class="service-grid">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <h4>🪖 Regulation Haircuts</h4>
                        <p>High and tight, just like in the Army!</p>
                        <span class="price">$12.99</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <h4>🍺 Dale's Dead Bug</h4>
                        <p>Professional pest control services</p>
                        <span class="price">$25.00</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <h4>🔧 Propane Accessories</h4>
                        <p>Sweet Lady Propane and her accessories</p>
                        <span class="price">$Sweet Deal</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-card vulnerable-service">
                        <h4>🏴‍☠️ Secret Military Files</h4>
                        <p>Classified documents from my Army days...</p>
                        <span class="price">🚨 TOP SECRET 🚨</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="challenge-hint">
                <h3>🔍 Something's Not Right Here...</h3>
                <p>Bill's been acting strange lately. He mentioned something about his server having some kind of "ghost" issue.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="army-memories">
                <h3>Bill's Army Days</h3>
                <div class="memory-box">
                    <p>"Back in the Army, we had protocols for everything. But sometimes..."</p>
                    <p><em>*Bill trails off and stares into the distance*</em></p>
                    <p>"Sometimes the protocols had vulnerabilities we didn't know about."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <footer class="footer">
            <p>© 2025 Bill Dauterive's Army Surplus & Barber Shop</p>
            <p>Located on Rainey Street, Arlen, Texas</p>
            <p><em>"That's a clean burning hell, I tell you what!"</em></p>
        </footer>
    </div>
    
    <div class="floating-propane">🔥</div>
</body>
</html>
